    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. A truly exceptional example for a discerning buyer who expects nothing less than perfection.",
